---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Student Stories - Real Journeys of Connection and Growth"
  description="Read inspiring stories from international students who found their London family, improved their English, and discovered confidence through our community."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-cream font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center mt-10">
      <h1
        class="font-sans font-bold text-5xl md:text-7xl text-charcoal leading-tight mb-6"
      >
        Real Stories
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
        Every journey is unique, but the destination is the same: finding your
        place, your voice, and your people in London.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181690/pexels-photo-1181690.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
            alt="Maria from Brazil"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold mb-2">
            From Brazil • 1 Year Journey
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl text-charcoal mb-6">
            Maria's Journey: From Scared to Confident
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
            "I arrived in London in January 2024 with basic English and zero
            friends. I was so scared to speak that I ordered food by pointing at
            pictures for my first two weeks. Everything changed when I found
            EnglishInLondon."
          </p>
          <blockquote
            class="border-l-4 border-earth pl-6 italic text-charcoal/80 mb-6"
          >
            "Within two weeks of joining the conversation circle, I had my first
            real English conversation over coffee. Six months later, I'm helping
            other new Brazilian students find their confidence too."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="font-sans font-bold text-2xl text-earth">15+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">New friends made</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="font-sans font-bold text-2xl text-earth">B2</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">English level achieved</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70">
            <strong>Maria's tip:</strong> "Don't wait to feel ready. Join a conversation
            group on your first week. The community will catch you when you stumble,
            and celebrate when you soar."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold mb-2">
            From Egypt • 10 Month Journey
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl text-charcoal mb-6">
            Ahmed's Journey: Finding His London Family
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
            "I came to London for my Master's degree, but I was struggling with
            academic English and feeling isolated. The buddy program didn't just
            improve my English – it gave me a brother."
          </p>
          <blockquote
            class="border-l-4 border-earth pl-6 italic text-charcoal/80 mb-6"
          >
            "My buddy James showed me his London – the hidden pubs, the weekend
            markets, the football culture. Now it's my London too. We still meet
            every week, even though my English is fluent now."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3">
              Ahmed's London Discovery List:
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal/70">
              <li>• Borough Market Saturday mornings</li>
              <li>• Arsenal matches at the local pub</li>
              <li>• Sunday roasts with James's family</li>
              <li>• Night photography walks along the Thames</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70">
            <strong>Ahmed's advice:</strong> "A buddy isn't just for English practice.
            They're your bridge to understanding British culture and feeling like
            you belong here."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1040880/pexels-photo-1040880.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
            alt="Ahmed from Egypt"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <img
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181686/pexels-photo-1181686.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
            alt="Yuki from Japan"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold mb-2">
            From Japan • 8 Month Journey
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl text-charcoal mb-6">
            Yuki's Journey: From Silent to Speaking Up
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
            "In Japan, I was good at English grammar and reading, but speaking
            terrified me. I thought I just needed to memorize more words. The
            community taught me that English is about connection, not
            perfection."
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-cream p-4 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">Before</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 space-y-1">
                <li>• Avoided group conversations</li>
                <li>• Studied alone for hours</li>
                <li>• Afraid of making mistakes</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-earth/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">After</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 space-y-1">
                <li>• Leads conversation groups</li>
                <li>• Learns through community events</li>
                <li>• Celebrates progress over perfection</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <blockquote
            class="border-l-4 border-earth pl-6 italic text-charcoal/80 mb-6"
          >
            "I discovered that my accent isn't something to hide – it's part of
            my story. Now I help other Japanese students embrace their voices
            too."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70">
            <strong>Yuki's wisdom:</strong> "Perfect English doesn't exist. Confident
            English does, and it comes from practice, patience, and people who believe
            in you."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-beige font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-script text-earth text-lg mb-4">
          More inspiring journeys
        </h2>
        <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal">
          Community Success Stories
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
            From Italy • 6 Months
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
            Marco's Business English Success
          </h4>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4 text-sm">
            "The business English practice group prepared me for job interviews.
            I landed my dream role at a London tech company after just 5 months
            of consistent practice."
          </p>
          <div class="text-earth text-sm font-medium">
            Now works at Google London →
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
            From Colombia • 1 Year
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
            Sofia's IELTS Achievement
          </h4>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4 text-sm">
            "The IELTS support group helped me go from band 5.5 to 8.0 in 8
            months. More importantly, I gained lifelong study partners who
            became my closest friends."
          </p>
          <div class="text-earth text-sm font-medium">
            Studying Medicine at King's College →
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
            From South Korea • 4 Months
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
            Jin's Confidence Transformation
          </h4>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4 text-sm">
            "I went from ordering food by pointing to speaking at university
            presentations confidently. The conversation circles made all the
            difference."
          </p>
          <div class="text-earth text-sm font-medium">
            Now studying at UCL →
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
            From France • 9 Months
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
            Amélie's Social Circle Growth
          </h4>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4 text-sm">
            "Through events and buddy programs, I built a diverse friend group
            from 12 different countries. London feels like home now, not just a
            place I study."
          </p>
          <div class="text-earth text-sm font-medium">
            Organizing her own events now →
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
            From Turkey • 7 Months
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
            Elif's Academic Success
          </h4>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4 text-sm">
            "The academic writing workshops and peer support helped me excel in
            my PhD program. I even published my first paper in English!"
          </p>
          <div class="text-earth text-sm font-medium">
            PhD candidate at Imperial →
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-earth font-semibold text-sm mb-2">
            From Thailand • 5 Months
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mb-3">
            Niran's Creative Expression
          </h4>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4 text-sm">
            "I found my voice through the creative writing group. Now I blog
            about my London experience and help other Thai students navigate
            life here."
          </p>
          <div class="text-earth text-sm font-medium">
            Started a popular blog →
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-sans font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-6">
        What will your story be?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-charcoal/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Every journey starts with a single step. Join our community and begin
        writing your own London success story today.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="bg-red text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-medium hover:bg-charcoal transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Start Your Journey
        </a>
        <a
          href="/community"
          class="border-2 border-earth text-earth px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-medium hover:bg-earth hover:text-white transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Explore Community
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
